get code:
=========
git clone https://github.com/PeterHjortLauritzen/CAM cam-idealized-tests
cd cam-idealized-tests
git checkout cam-idealized-tests

setup:
======
cd my_scripts
module load python/3.7.12
open "FKESSLER.sh" and set correct account number: set PBS_ACCOUNT="P93300642"
source FKSESSLER (will show you arguments required); 

here is what I run:

source FKESSLER.sh mpasa120_mpasa120 /glade/p/cgd/amp/pel/src/cam-idealized-tests cam-idealized-tests

